»A thousand feathers« 🪶
Actually I've planned to draw something else, 😄but I was inspired by the cutest little bird I've ever seen which we found a few days ago 🥺 (swipe to see the video👉). He was lying on the ground after he probably fell out of his nest. Based on his fluffy hairstyle, I assume he was probably too young to fly. 🖤
We put him in a nearby tree and his mom (or dad) found him there a few minutes later.🙏😃
